<div id="template">
    <p id="text">
        Members of the European Parliament personally choose their assistants and can ask to terminate the contract if and when they so wish.
        This is why victims of sexual harassment nearly never report incidents of concern.
        This is inacceptable! <br>Sign this petition to <br><span>Ban sexual harassment in the European Parliament!<span>
    </p>
    <img id="signPetitionPic" src="/public/euparliament.jpg" alt="">

    <form class="user" action='/signPetition' method="post">
        <input id="first" type="text" placeholder="Enter first name" name="first" value="{{first}}">
        <input id="last" type="text" placeholder="Enter last name" name="last" value="{{last}}">
        <input type="hidden" name="img">
        <input type="hidden" name="_csrf" value="{{csrfToken}}">
        <button id="submit">Submit</button>
    </form>
    <p id="sign">Please sign here:</p>
    <canvas id="canvas" width="500" height="150"></canvas>
</div>
